    The restaurant serves speciality from Marseille, whose the
    <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bouillabaisse">famous
    <em lang="fr">Bouillabaisse</em></a>!</p>
    <figure>
      <img src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/24/Bullabessa.jpg"
           alt="Bouillabaisse" />
      <figcaption>Bouillabaisse, from
      <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bouillabaisse#mediaviewer/File:Bullabessa.jpg">Wikipédia</a>.</figcaption>
    </figure>
    <figure>
      <img src="http://lechateausormiou.fr/images/slide1.jpg"
           alt="View from the restaurant" />
      <figcaption>View from the restaurant:
      <a href="http://lechateausormiou.fr/">Le château Sormiou</a>.</figcaption>
