    <p>This year, the goodies were a <em lang="en">pétanque</em> ball with “Hoa
    Apex'14” engraved on its surface.</p>
    <figure>
      <img src="https://farm4.staticflickr.com/3895/14956577616_9c97e6fb22_c.jpg" />
