    <h2>Conclusion</h2>
    
    <p>This second edition of Hoa Apex has been a success. Hoa is growing like never
    before and we see concrete results. New projects are going to be deployed, along
    with a better communication (you will see it on this blog by yourself). In
    short: thanks a lot for your presence, usages and feedbacks! Keep going!</p>
  </article>
